(## 2. Product Overview) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(### What this application does) Tj
0 -14 Td
(MockMind is an AI-assisted interview preparation platform where authenticated users can:) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Generate role/difficulty/language-specific interview question sets) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Answer theory questions via voice recording \(with AI transcription\)) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Answer coding questions via text editor) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Submit sessions for AI evaluation and score calculation) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Ask a built-in concept chatbot for interview-focused explanations) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Review historical sessions and feedback) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
