(## 10. Authentication & Security) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(### JWT usage) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- User and admin auth both use JWT signed with `JWT_SECRET`.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- User token TTL: `7d`.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Admin token TTL: `12h` and includes `role: "admin"` claim.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(### Password hashing) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- User and admin passwords are hashed with `bcryptjs` before storage.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- User registration salt rounds: 10 \(`bcrypt.genSalt\(10\)`\).) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Admin seeding uses `bcrypt.hash\(password, 10\)`.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(### Middleware) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- `protect`: validates user token and attaches user document to `req.user`.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- `protectAdmin`: validates token, enforces `role === admin`, checks `isActive`.) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- `notFound` and `errorHandler` normalize error responses.) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(### Role-based access) Tj
ET
