(### Challenges) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Enforcing structured AI outputs \(JSON for generation/evaluation and readable text for chatbot\)) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Handling mixed input modes \(voice + code\) in one session lifecycle) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Keeping user and admin auth flows separated while sharing JWT base logic) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Managing async dependencies \(transcription, evaluation, email\) with graceful fallback behavior) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Building analytics endpoints over evolving collection naming) Tj
0 -14 Td
(\(`practisesessions`/`practicesessions`\)) Tj
0 -14 Td
() Tj
0 -14 Td
(### Learnings) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Prompt design and defensive parsing are essential for production-facing AI pipelines) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- GridFS is effective when audio artifacts must stay close to session records in MongoDB) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Role-claim-based JWT strategy keeps admin boundary explicit and lightweight) Tj
0 -14 Td
(- Product quality depends heavily on response formatting and UX, not just model output) Tj
